{"content":"<div id=\"Ps.128\" class=\"chapter\">\n<h3 class=\"d\">上行之诗。</h3>\n<h3 class=\"s\">顺从耶和华的报偿</h3>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v1\"><sup id=\"Ps.128.1\" class=\"v1\">1</sup>凡敬畏耶和华、</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v1\">遵行他道的人有福了！</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v2\"><sup id=\"Ps.128.2\" class=\"v2\">2</sup>你要吃劳碌得来的；</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v2\">你要享福，凡事顺利。</span></p>\n<p class=\"b\"></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v3\"><sup id=\"Ps.128.3\" class=\"v3\">3</sup>你妻子在你内室，好像多结果子的葡萄树；</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v3\">你儿女围绕你的桌子，如同橄榄树苗。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v4\"><sup id=\"Ps.128.4\" class=\"v4\">4</sup>看哪，敬畏耶和华的人</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v4\">必要这样蒙福！</span></p>\n<p class=\"b\"></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v5\"><sup id=\"Ps.128.5\" class=\"v5\">5</sup>愿耶和华从<span class=\"pn\">锡安</span>赐福给你！</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v5\">愿你一生一世看见<span class=\"pn\">耶路撒冷</span>兴旺！</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v6\"><sup id=\"Ps.128.6\" class=\"v6\">6</sup>愿你看见</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v6\">你的子子孙孙！</span></p>\n<p class=\"b\"></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v6\">愿平安归于<span class=\"pn\">以色列</span>！</span></p>\n</div>\n"}